from fpdf import FPDF
from datetime import datetime

# Create a PDF class
class VetInvoicePDF(FPDF):
    def header(self):
        self.set_font("Arial", "B", 14)
        self.cell(0, 10, "Northwest Rankin County Animal Hospital", ln=True, align="C")
        self.set_font("Arial", "", 12)
        self.cell(0, 10, "106 Autumn Ridge Pl, Flowood, MS 39232", ln=True, align="C")
        self.cell(0, 10, "(601) 555-0191", ln=True, align="C")
        self.ln(10)

    def footer(self):
        self.set_y(-15)
        self.set_font("Arial", "I", 8)
        self.cell(0, 10, "Thank you for trusting us with Angel's care!", 0, 0, "C")

# Create the PDF
pdf = VetInvoicePDF()
pdf.add_page()
pdf.set_font("Arial", "B", 12)
pdf.cell(0, 10, "INVOICE", ln=True, align="C")
pdf.ln(10)

# Invoice Info
pdf.set_font("Arial", "", 11)
pdf.cell(0, 10, f"Date: {datetime.now().strftime('%B %d, %Y')}", ln=True)
pdf.cell(0, 10, "Client Name: Brooke", ln=True)
pdf.cell(0, 10, "Patient Name: Angel", ln=True)
pdf.cell(0, 10, "Species: Feline (Cat)", ln=True)
pdf.cell(0, 10, "Breed: Domestic Longhair", ln=True)
pdf.cell(0, 10, "Color: White", ln=True)
pdf.cell(0, 10, "Sex: Female", ln=True)
pdf.ln(10)

# Table Headers
pdf.set_font("Arial", "B", 11)
pdf.cell(100, 10, "Description", border=1)
pdf.cell(30, 10, "Qty", border=1)
pdf.cell(30, 10, "Unit Price", border=1)
pdf.cell(30, 10, "Total", border=1, ln=True)

# Table Content
pdf.set_font("Arial", "", 11)
services = [
    ("Basic Physical Exam", 1, 55.00),
    ("Clinic Sanitation Fee", 1, 5.00)
]

subtotal = 0
for desc, qty, price in services:
    total = qty * price
    subtotal += total
    pdf.cell(100, 10, desc, border=1)
    pdf.cell(30, 10, str(qty), border=1)
    pdf.cell(30, 10, f"${price:.2f}", border=1)
    pdf.cell(30, 10, f"${total:.2f}", border=1, ln=True)

# Totals
sales_tax = subtotal * 0.07
total_due = subtotal + sales_tax
pdf.set_font("Arial", "B", 11)
pdf.cell(160, 10, "Subtotal", border=1)
pdf.cell(30, 10, f"${subtotal:.2f}", border=1, ln=True)
pdf.cell(160, 10, "Sales Tax (7%)", border=1)
pdf.cell(30, 10, f"${sales_tax:.2f}", border=1, ln=True)
pdf.cell(160, 10, "Amount Due", border=1)
pdf.cell(30, 10, f"${total_due:.2f}", border=1, ln=True)

# Save PDF
pdf_path = "/mnt/data/Northwest_Rankin_Invoice_Angel.pdf"
pdf.output(pdf_path)

pdf_path
